this is the chapel of my school which is the holiest and most peaceful spot in this school area. this chapel is quite famous in bogor, sometimes there are some brides choose this chapel for their wedding ceremony, usually they are the alumnus of regina pacis. my school's choir usually use the chapel for practicing too. I really like the architecture of this chapel. the floor are decorated with some tribal patterns and there are a lot of windows inside. the atmosphere in this chapel is so nice and i cant find any flaw from this chapel, so we as the students should take care of it so that the next generations still can use the chapel comfortably. #XIMIPA5
